name: My Favorite Fantasy
description:
I look at you and see what I want to see
You are my favorite fantasy 
I am inside it every night and day
From you I can’t escape

Cause you dear are the one I've been waiting for 
Of this I am sure 

The breath is better after struggling to breathe
And my lungs are hungry for air
Release your grip from my neck slowly now
Return it where it belongs 

Breathe in breathe out nice and slow 
Let the moment last 
Feel the future fade away 
Present into past

I would move mountains I would part seas
Just to have you closer to me
I’d believe in myself just like you do 
But you leave me nothing 
Because of the truth 

You still are the one I’ve been searching for
Of this I am sure
And I’ll stand with 
my heart in my hand at your door
Just bleeding for you 

Oh what could you have decided to do 
Maybe I know exactly what you’re going through
